    <section class="">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="heading-1 fs-35 black-1 text-center mt-30">
          Let’s build your home together!
        </div>
        <div class="mt-20 text-center sub-heading black-1 fs-18 lh-30">
          Building a new home and furnishing your own space is a reflection of your personality. It’s one of the most delightful
          things you do! Here are a few questions that people often ask us. If you have any other questions, you can reach us by
          clicking on the contact us button.
        </div>
        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingOne">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseOne">
                Can I sit at home & revamp my home?
              </h2>
            </div>

            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                Yes, absolutely! Our expert team will understand your space. We endeavour to transform your space with our home design
                services.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingTwo">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                What are the sizes of your Bed Covers?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                Our Bed Covers are standard 90 X 108”. We also do specialised measurements in 100 X 10”
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingThree">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Do you customise Bed Linens?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                Yes, we do customise Bed Linens according to the size preference of fabric & design of the clients.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingFour">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseFour">
                Can Curtains be washed?
              </h2>
            </div>
          
            <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                It’s safest to give your curtains to a professional laundry.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingFive">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseFive">
                Can Upholstery be washed?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                No, sticked upholstery cannot be washed. However loose covers can be washed by hand in cold water.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingSix">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseSix">
              Do you do customisation?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseSix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                We offer specialised services for medium & large sized orders. We have worked with reputed interior designers and
                reputed hotels to fulfill their bedding and bath needs.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingSeven">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                What are sheer curtains?
              </h2>
            </div>
          
            <div id="collapseSeven" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                It's an undeniable fact that curtains & drapes possess an elegance unrivalled by other window treatments. Sheer curtains
                or sheers are lightweight, easy to hang fabrics that instantly add a hazy, dreamy quality to a room without dominating
                the decor. Right from enveloping the windows and softening the lighting to adding an infusion of style into your
                interior decor.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingEight">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseEight">
                How does upholstery play a role in the look & feel of the space?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseEight" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                Once the design is finalised, the next step is selecting the right fabric for the furniture and space. This stage is
                very important to detail which makes the space look elegant, friendly & comfortable. While there are endless choices one
                needs to be practical in their selection for the right space. The right upholstery is an investment, so it is very
                important to find a fabric you will love for a long run & yet make you comfortable.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingNine">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseNine">
                Can leather sofas be reupholstered?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseNine" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNine" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingTen">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseTen">
                Do your Duvet Covers come with Pillow Case?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTen" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTen" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
          
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-head" id="headingEleven">
              <h2 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseEleven" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="collapseEleven">
                Do you provide interior Suggestions?
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseEleven" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEleven" data-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="card-body">
          
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-50 mt-50">
      <div class="container text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
        <a href="<%= contact_us_path %>">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-4">Contact Us</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%= render "shared/call_back" %>
    
      <%= render "shared/footer" %>
  </div>

  

  <style>
    .accordion {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .accordion .card {
      border-radius: 16px !important;
      background: #FFF;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .accordion .card h2 {
      background: url('/images/faq/acc-down.png') no-repeat calc(100% - 10px) center;
      background-size: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      color: #3A3A3A;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .accordion .card h2.collapsed {
      background-image: url('/images/faq/acc-down.png');
    }

    .accordion .card-body {
      color: #515151;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 30px;
    }
  </style>